  • Constructor Details

    • EdenCommand

      public EdenCommand(String name, EdenModule parent_module)
      An Eden command with the specified name and tied to the given module. Commands tied to a module are categorized with the /eden helpall command.
      Parameters:
      name - The name of the command, as in "/name".
      parent_module - The module this command is tied to.

    • EdenCommand

      public EdenCommand(String name, List<String> aliases, EdenModule parent_module)
      An Eden command with the specified name, a list of potential aliases, and tied to the given module. Commands tied to a module are categorized with the /eden helpall command.
      Parameters:
      name - The name of the command, as in "/name".
      aliases - A list of potential aliases for this command.
      parent_module - parent_module The module this command is tied to.

    • edencommand_help

      public void edencommand_help(org.bukkit.command.CommandSender sender, String commandLabel, String[] args)
      A shared help command, always present with every Eden command.

      Should not be invoked manually, unless linked to another command.

      Parameters:
      sender - The command sender.
      commandLabel - The label used for this command.
      args - A list of arguments in string format.

    • addBranch

      protected TabCompleter addBranch(String... labels)
      Adds a branch to this command's TabComplete tree. While this class does not implement TabCompleter, it does abide by the contract of such classes.
      Parameters:
      labels - The labels of branches to add
      Returns:
      A TabCompleteBranch of only one branch is specified, or a TabCompleteMultiBranch if two or more branches are specified
      Throws:
      UnsupportedOperationException - If zero branches are supplied
